snippet.title: Slaughter Me Street: 1999 - Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2922990/Slaughter_Me_Street_1999/

Hello Slaughtermenauts! We are pleased to announce that the Slaughter Me Street: 1999 Demo is available now on Steam. Go check it out, let us know what you think, and give us a wishlist! 

Full game coming this Fall!

Follow our Steam curator page too for Steam updates!
https://store.steampowered.com/curator/45128015-Impulse-Game-Studios-LLC./
